pos_examples: Now, cut board socket into part object_260 using highspeed-saw fire with awood star_213, surface bastion, changing size from aboardsize yew to aboardsize yew_59 via intermediate sizes aboardsize yew_59_42 and aboardsize yew_59_42_82.
(cut-board-large socket object_260 fire star_213 bastion yew yew_59_42_82 yew_59_42 yew_59)

Once you are done, please saw board socket into medium part object_260 using saw roof_11 with awood star_213, surface bastion, changing size from aboardsize yew to aboardsize yew_59 through aboardsize yew_35.
(do-saw-medium socket object_260 roof_11 star_213 bastion yew yew_35 yew_59)

First, unload board socket from highspeed-saw fire and then do grind on part object_260 using grinder rain to change surface from surface bastion to verysmooth, color from acolour kumquat to natural, and treatment from treatmentstatus teddy to treatmentstatus teddy_81.

(unload-highspeed-saw socket fire)
(do-grind object_260 rain bastion kumquat teddy teddy_81)
The next step is to do glaze on part object_260 using glazer kumquat_8 to change color to acolour kumquat.
